{"by":"sparin9","id":47761036,"kids":[47761050],"parent":47756569,"text":"This is a genuinely delightful project. The graph-based approach to navigating the Mahābhārata and Rāmāyaṇa feels really natural — these epics are fundamentally about relationships and webs of consequence, so exploring them through a character graph rather than linear text makes a lot of sense.<p>The Crimson Dusk theme is a nice touch too. Looking forward to seeing how the data coverage grows over time!","time":1776138583,"type":"comment"}